    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1717746186\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br>Food Empire is an economic strategy game in which you will be able to build your own restaurant business. You will begin with one small diner in a location of your choosing, and in time you will be able to expand to different areas. The game lets you take control of many aspects of managing restaurants, and allows for some personal customization of your brand's look.<br><br>It goes like this:<br><br>First you choose a building to buy, while considering various different factors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/fc87230a42ce91695c8501a28f38cf43.poster.avif?t=1717746186\" width=728 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/fc87230a42ce91695c8501a28f38cf43.webm?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/fc87230a42ce91695c8501a28f38cf43.mp4?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Not its time to renovate. Sell all the junk you find and choose the look of walls and floors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/e7b96e6f4b3ecdc4dd6a61f68d026107.poster.avif?t=1717746186\" width=728 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/e7b96e6f4b3ecdc4dd6a61f68d026107.webm?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/e7b96e6f4b3ecdc4dd6a61f68d026107.mp4?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Design the restaurant yourself. In time you will be able to unlock many additional interior items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/7607f17daf0e481053ba0f6d342cddfe.poster.avif?t=1717746186\" width=728 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/7607f17daf0e481053ba0f6d342cddfe.webm?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/7607f17daf0e481053ba0f6d342cddfe.mp4?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Pick your staff according to their skill level and payment expectations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/bb5e561a2e5a398254256741baf484ee.poster.avif?t=1717746186\" width=728 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/bb5e561a2e5a398254256741baf484ee.webm?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/bb5e561a2e5a398254256741baf484ee.mp4?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Finally - feed your customers!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/c4b71ca58cf385a4af0ee536ed316b05.poster.avif?t=1717746186\" width=728 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/c4b71ca58cf385a4af0ee536ed316b05.webm?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877520/extras/c4b71ca58cf385a4af0ee536ed316b05.mp4?t=1717746186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In time new opportunities will open up and allow for branching out into different food businesses. Manage your finances, take care of your customer's needs and slowly but surely you will build your Food Empire.",
